---
title: Spicy Sausage Chilli. with Homemade Tortilla Chips
description: At the HelloFresh Farm, we like to pack as much flavour as possible into our dishes, in as short a time scale as we can. Our trick in achieving this is to use sausage meat already packed with delicious ingredients.
This little trick gives you the best tasting dish in minimal time! You are welcome!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spicy-sausage-chilli-wk43-db6e7da4.jpg
